---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "HomeProjectHub privacy policy. We use localStorage for saved rooms and Google AdSense for advertising. We do not collect personal data.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6">
    <header class="border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">Last updated: {new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0]}</p>
    </header>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>HomeProjectHub ("we", "us") operates the website at homeprojecthub.com. This privacy policy explains how we handle data when you use our calculators and tools.</p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-2">Local Storage</h2>
        <p>We use your browser's localStorage to save room dimensions you enter in our calculators. This data never leaves your device and is not transmitted to our servers. You can clear this data at any time by clearing your browser's site data or using the delete button on the Saved Rooms page.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-2">Google AdSense</h2>
        <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="underline hover:text-neutral-900 dark:hover:text-neutral-100" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>. For more information about how Google uses data, visit <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" class="underline hover:text-neutral-900 dark:hover:text-neutral-100" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy & Terms</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-2">Analytics</h2>
        <p>We may use privacy-focused analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns. We do not collect personally identifiable information through analytics.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-2">Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy questions, contact us through the website. This page may be updated from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or regulatory requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
